Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.13,0:00:03.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, all you viewers out there!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.95,0:00:07.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When you're watchin' Fairy Tail, make \Nsure to keep the room nice and bright,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.12,0:00:09.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and sit back from the screen, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.59,0:00:13.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Previously on Fairy Tail:
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.75,0:00:16.53,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,With Natsu and the others joining \Nin the Battle of Fairy Tail,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.53,0:00:18.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,and the Raijin Tribe completely defeated,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.28,0:00:21.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,all that's left is to stop \NLaxus's Thunder Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.11,0:00:23.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But just then, the master collapsed!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.56,0:00:46.37,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo Ho! Steer that rudder! Hard to port!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.37,0:00:49.92,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo Ho! Our high-flyin' lives are every which way!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.56,0:01:02.61,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,When the sun goes down, there's a bon voyage bash.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.83,0:01:08.15,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,It ain't sad at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.15,0:01:15.35,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we're alive, we'll meet again somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.35,0:01:19.64,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Blast straight through a headwind, set off!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.64,0:01:24.44,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay strong until the tears dry up! A man gotta be tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.44,0:01:29.15,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Friends, friends, laugh one day!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.15,0:01:33.87,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,As proof of our strong, strong bonds!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.87,0:01:41.77,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, grab that map to the shining future!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.93,0:02:03.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy, look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.50,0:02:07.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Freed vs. Mirajane: Both removed \Nthemselves from contention?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.12,0:02:10.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So that light from before was... I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.24,0:02:11.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Demon...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.80,0:02:14.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I kinda wish I'd seen it, \Nbut then again maybe not...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.61,0:02:17.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, the Raijin Tribe have been wiped out!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.50,0:02:18.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.83,0:02:25.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But then there's the Thunder Palace: Thunder \Nlacrima that will attack the entire city...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.88,0:02:27.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.87,0:02:31.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as they're protected \Nby the Body Link magic,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:35.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,attacking them will end \Nup damaging ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.73,0:02:38.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's not much time left either.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.93,0:02:41.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And not being able to get the \Npeople in the city to evacuate...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.68,0:02:45.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.79,0:02:47.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.89,0:02:50.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Your magic power hasn't recovered yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.86,0:02:52.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't push yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.44,0:02:56.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But there has to be something we can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.06,0:02:58.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.20,0:03:02.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you now, Natsu, Erza?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.19,0:03:08.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Clash at Kardia Cathedral!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.20,0:03:15.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you, Laxus?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.33,0:03:16.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.39,0:03:19.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Show yourself, Laxus!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.01,0:03:23.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The Thunder Palace... Rendering the \Njudgment of the god of thunder.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.45,0:03:25.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only 10 minutes until it activates.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.13,0:03:28.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Laxus really serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.30,0:03:31.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But it'll work out, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.25,0:03:35.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We still have Erza and Natsu... \NAnd Gajeel's there too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.15,0:03:38.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! And wasn't Mystogan around?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.17,0:03:40.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I've never seen him...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.34,0:03:43.98,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder who that could be?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.78,0:03:53.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is the old fool?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.23,0:03:56.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Poluchka-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.10,0:03:57.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.76,0:03:59.79,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I asked you where he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.20,0:04:01.72,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's in the inside clinic!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.97,0:04:07.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, excuse me but... Right now he's...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.49,0:04:08.77,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.77,0:04:09.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I came.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.11,0:04:14.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you came to treat the master?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.95,0:04:18.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.22,0:04:37.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring Laxus here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.52,0:04:42.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Bring that fool of a boy who's playing \Naround while his grandfather lies gravely ill.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.71,0:04:46.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Gravely ill? You're not serious, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.84,0:04:49.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just bring him... Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.50,0:04:53.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't have long.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.10,0:05:05.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.50,0:05:06.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.20,0:05:11.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You promised to watch Fantasia \Ntogether with me this year, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:14.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,How about that, Laxus?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.88,0:05:17.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Those are Fairy Tail wizards!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.71,0:05:23.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I remembering these stupid things now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.36,0:05:31.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus... You aren't going to \Nparticipate in the Fantasia?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.79,0:05:35.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you talkin' about, old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.30,0:05:42.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I was little, everyone's \Nalways seen me as your grandson!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.36,0:05:45.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter what I do, I'm \Nalways, "Makarov's grandson"!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.07,0:05:50.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I'm always, "The master of Fairy Tail's \Ngrandson," I can never get credit for what I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.00,0:05:53.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That really depends on your point of view.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.56,0:05:59.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anyone in the world who \Nreally gets the credit they deserve?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.79,0:06:04.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,All he said was that he was uncomfortable, \Nand then you went and shamed him even more!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.04,0:06:06.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.35,0:06:08.58,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have any sympathy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.50,0:06:13.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.05,0:06:16.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd you expel my dad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.47,0:06:21.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Say something!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.69,0:06:23.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.03,0:06:27.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ivan... He brought harm to the guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.93,0:06:31.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he did a lot of stupid stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.19,0:06:34.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, he's your son!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.55,0:06:35.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He's family!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.58,0:06:38.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Even be they family,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.88,0:06:43.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot allow those who threaten the lives \Nof their comrades to remain in the same guild.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.26,0:06:47.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how my predecessor protected \NFairy Tail before it passed to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.05,0:06:50.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That is Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.59,0:06:53.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Then kick me out too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.54,0:06:57.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll join the guild my dad started up...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.52,0:06:59.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,...and crush you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.20,0:07:01.36,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He started a guild?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.69,0:07:05.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You know where Ivan is now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.47,0:07:07.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,As if you actually care.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.51,0:07:08.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice try.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:10.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait, Laxus!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.95,0:07:16.96,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He left here in the possession of \Ninformation that could harm Fairy Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.30,0:07:21.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to find him, or \NFairy Tail's in trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.03,0:07:24.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's rich, coming from the \None that threw him out...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.86,0:07:26.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.85,0:07:29.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,One day I'll surpass you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.23,0:07:30.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not for my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.88,0:07:33.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But for myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.66,0:07:36.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For me to become my own man!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.88,0:07:43.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The time is ripe.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.59,0:07:46.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Old man, I will surpass you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.78,0:07:52.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Six minutes until the \NThunder Palace activates.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.44,0:07:55.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he not gonna step down?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.90,0:07:58.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What a stubborn old fool, as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.43,0:08:13.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You came, Mystogan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:22.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think you'd be \Nparticipating in this game!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.03,0:08:25.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If you call off the Thunder Palace right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.09,0:08:29.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,it is still possible to pass this \Noff as merely entertainment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.09,0:08:30.91,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So blissfully ignorant...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.91,0:08:38.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you heard the rumors figuring who \Nis the strongest in Fairy Tail, you or me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.95,0:08:42.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I don't really care, \Naren't you forgetting Erza?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.15,0:08:43.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Her? Not a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.73,0:08:46.71,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She's on the right track, but still weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.06,0:08:50.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza, weak?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.00,0:08:53.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you truly that blind?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.30,0:08:57.02,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying I recognize your skills, Mystogan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.40,0:09:03.09,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder which one of us is really \Nthe strongest in Fairy Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.09,0:09:08.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If that is all your eyes can see, I wonder \Nwho is the one so blissfully ignorant?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.40,0:09:10.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's settle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.60,0:09:12.23,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll decide who's the strongest!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.17,0:09:14.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mystogan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.35,0:09:17.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, another...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.95,0:09:28.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The church?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.16,0:09:29.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Kardia Cathedral?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.20,0:09:39.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did you learn of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.81,0:09:45.89,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? That's quite rare to see you panic...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.89,0:09:47.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did I find out?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.50,0:09:51.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows? Maybe I'll \Ntell you if you beat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.79,0:09:55.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You will regret this, Laxus.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.94,0:10:01.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You will now witness magic that \Nyou have never seen before!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.11,0:10:02.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.78,0:10:05.12,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me your best shot, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.37,0:10:07.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you just how different we two are!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.14,0:10:18.59,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Tower of Babel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.39,0:10:29.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.19,0:10:31.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.35,0:10:32.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,The entire cathedral?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.13,0:10:54.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is this magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.12,0:11:14.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What a joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.35,0:11:20.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You thought this illusion would \Nactually work on me, Mystogan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.15,0:11:22.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.86,0:11:25.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But you noticed just a bit too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.87,0:11:32.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.10,0:11:34.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Five Layered Magic Circle, Sacred Song!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.09,0:11:40.46,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one of us is the one who didn't notice?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.92,0:11:43.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.69,0:12:02.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,He slipped out?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.98,0:12:14.66,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You ain't bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.29,0:12:16.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.54,0:12:18.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.60,0:12:19.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.41,0:12:20.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You got out?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.26,0:12:24.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And, who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.50,0:12:25.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mystogan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.93,0:12:30.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You let down your guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.25,0:12:48.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.94,0:12:50.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.80,0:12:55.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.34,0:12:57.21,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.21,0:13:00.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a familiar face?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.56,0:13:04.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.84,0:13:08.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Mystogan... or Jellal?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.60,0:13:20.84,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Jellal...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.22,0:13:26.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza, I especially didn't want you to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.30,0:13:31.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not Jellal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.74,0:13:35.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I know of him, but I am not him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.40,0:13:43.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.93,0:13:45.05,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I leave the rest to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.32,0:13:46.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.47,0:13:50.78,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I'm all confused...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.78,0:13:52.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll deal with that later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.15,0:13:54.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus, I came here to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.75,0:13:57.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza, you'll let me handle him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.32,0:14:00.44,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.06,0:14:07.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go making ugly faces, Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.65,0:14:09.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now come at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.31,0:14:12.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Laxus!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.32,0:14:16.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I said that {\i1}I'd{\i0} fight you, bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.29,0:14:18.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You were here, Natsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.40,0:14:23.83,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't underestimate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.34,0:14:33.39,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now fight me, Laxus!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.50,0:14:35.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.52,0:14:41.81,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You are so annoying, always \Ncharging straight in!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.96,0:14:45.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost, small fry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.15,0:14:51.11,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Talons of the Fire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.28,0:14:56.24,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.61,0:14:59.16,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.05,0:15:05.17,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You ain't gettin' away, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.49,0:15:10.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You think I was running?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.26,0:15:12.13,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a chance to take the top spot!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.00,0:15:23.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll crush you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.86,0:15:33.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.78,0:15:39.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I must forget about Jellal... I \Nmean, Mystogan for the time being.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.47,0:15:40.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, it's Laxus.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.54,0:15:42.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Requip!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.36,0:15:48.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.62,0:15:51.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What are those things \Nfloating in the sky, Laxus?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.88,0:15:53.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Thunder Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.75,0:15:55.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you heard of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.67,0:15:59.69,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You're seriously intending to \Nattack Magnolia, you fiend?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.61,0:16:04.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a new rule!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.90,0:16:07.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It really pains my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.09,0:16:11.74,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You vile fiend!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.74,0:16:13.99,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Only two minutes left.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.70,0:16:16.82,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, destroy them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.82,0:16:18.61,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.61,0:16:22.55,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Or I mean, if I do that, then \NI'll get destroyed myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.55,0:16:23.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.66,0:16:26.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So that means, Body Link magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.54,0:16:27.86,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.86,0:16:30.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No one can touch those lacrima!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.67,0:16:31.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.20,0:16:37.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll destroy you with my lightning as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.01,0:16:37.97,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Requip!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.26,0:16:41.18,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.18,0:16:43.01,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Thunder Empress armor?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.01,0:16:46.60,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You seriously think that'll \Nprotect you from my lightning?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.04,0:16:51.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just about defense, Laxus!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.95,0:17:05.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just try and block this, Erza!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.26,0:17:08.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.95,0:17:14.30,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,When two wizards of the same type clash, \Nthe factors that determine the outcome...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.30,0:17:15.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoever has the highest magical power...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.75,0:17:19.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And their technique and experience, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.51,0:17:21.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And, their heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.15,0:17:24.73,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You should have learned this from the master!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.73,0:17:26.50,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I learned.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.50,0:17:29.42,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I learned that the most \Nimportant thing is power.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.95,0:17:32.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It's villains like you who...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.80,0:17:36.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Erza, stopped gettin' all revved up!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.10,0:17:38.49,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I'll be the one to take on Laxus!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.80,0:17:44.56,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I'll believe in you then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.16,0:17:49.80,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.63,0:17:54.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, are you going to \Nstop the Thunder Palace?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.08,0:17:58.38,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.69,0:18:01.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Just destroying one risks your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.03,0:18:05.93,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And right now there are \Ncountless lacrima up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.93,0:18:07.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no time either!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.10,0:18:10.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will destroy them all at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.40,0:18:11.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.98,0:18:15.07,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And if you did, you really wouldn't survive!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.52,0:18:18.75,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,But the city would be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.81,0:18:23.95,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop Laxus, Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.20,0:18:25.37,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.37,0:18:27.25,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you gonna break the rules of the game?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.25,0:18:30.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I should believe in you too, Erza.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.74,0:18:38.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mean what's possible or impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.62,0:18:40.76,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Believing in you coming back safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.27,0:18:42.51,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.96,0:18:44.87,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Mine is a life that you saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.25,0:18:47.03,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't go throwing it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.93,0:18:49.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.14,0:18:51.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Roar of the Fire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.30,0:18:57.32,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will defeat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.17,0:19:02.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You little brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.49,0:19:13.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Blades, lend me the power to \Nprotect the city of Magnolia.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.67,0:19:16.34,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, to everyone in Fairy Tail...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.67,0:19:18.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Lend me your power!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.92,0:19:22.90,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you just hear Erza's voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.90,0:19:25.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I heard it, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.65,0:19:27.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She said to lend her our power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.40,0:19:28.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Aye.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.87,0:19:33.10,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,She wants us to help her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.10,0:19:35.70,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not like you, Erza.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.18,0:19:38.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.40,0:19:45.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can get Erza's voice to reach \Neveryone like it reached me...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.19,0:19:51.26,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,For that, I need Warren's help!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.46,0:19:55.67,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Dazzling Blaze of the Fire Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.01,0:20:03.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You should realize this, Natsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.76,0:20:07.43,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you see how pitiful \Nthis guild has become?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.99,0:20:12.27,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I will change the guild!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.50,0:20:18.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,And to do that, I must become the master!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.20,0:20:30.41,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.41,0:20:34.00,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Now of all times, we can't find anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.69,0:20:37.08,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Warren Rocko!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.08,0:20:39.06,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you there, Warren?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.93,0:20:46.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Still a minute and thirty seconds \Nuntil the Thunder Palace activates?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.23,0:20:49.40,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you doing, old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.83,0:20:52.68,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you know what'll happen to the city?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.13,0:20:58.31,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,No need to be so worried, Laxus!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.11,0:21:01.35,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,'Cause nothing's gonna happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.35,0:21:02.65,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.65,0:21:06.15,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,You won't get anything \Nfrom destroying the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.69,0:21:09.62,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So now you're gettin' upset \Ncause you can't get out of it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.25,0:21:14.29,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, Erza will stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.97,0:21:18.85,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,It ain't so easy to stick \Nto your guns, is it Laxus?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.21,0:21:23.28,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Like you have a clue!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.73,0:21:47.57,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,100!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.65,0:21:54.04,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, not enough...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.46,0:22:17.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.23,0:22:33.69,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,That time we laughed, saying "we're both like each other,"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.09,0:22:43.87,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,we even kindly overlooked the little lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.70,0:22:49.97,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,If we lose a place to go back to together, I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.20,0:22:58.72,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I'll protect that smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.10,0:23:03.16,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,The meetings and partings numerous as the stars in the sky...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.16,0:23:05.61,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,All the things I don't want to lose...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.61,0:23:10.29,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now I feel like I don't need any of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.29,0:23:15.44,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,I just want to see you by my side,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.72,0:23:21.07,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,all my happiness and sadness.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.07,0:23:23.55,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.55,0:23:26.15,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start our tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.15,0:23:30.65,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do it like we've just been reborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.65,0:23:36.20,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,Like flowers blown in a summer wind,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.20,0:23:44.90,Song Subtitles,,0000,0000,0000,,let us bloom brightly in this instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.85,0:24:00.54,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsu, it seems like we'll get another \NDragon Slayer joining the fray next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.54,0:24:03.20,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I'm fine on my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.20,0:24:06.33,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just gonna dilute my star presence!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.33,0:24:07.88,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's already pretty weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.88,0:24:11.64,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey now... I'm workin' so hard here!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.64,0:24:13.94,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Working hard to suck?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.94,0:24:16.14,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: Triple Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.47,0:24:18.47,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,So there's me, and Gajeel, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.47,0:24:19.52,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, who's the other one?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.52,0:24:23.45,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be that I am actually \Nthe Fish Dragon Slayer...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.45,0:24:24.48,Main Dialog,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, no.
